-- 
2011-08-24T10:29:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-24/new-africa-properties-to-list-in-botswana-on-sept-28-after-share-sale.html
New Africa Properties Ltd. will list
its stock in Gaborone, Botswana on Sept. 28 after selling 130
million pula in a private placing, the companyâ€™s adviser said in
an e-mailed statement today.  New Africa is also selling 20 million pula ($19 million) of
shares, or 10 million units at 2 pula each, to the public in an
offer that opens today and closes Sept. 14, Imara Botswana,
which is advising the company, said. The company is expected to
have a market value of 1.2 billion pula.  New Africa has 58 properties in Botswana and eight in
 Namibia , Imara said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
